#. <section class="sutta" id="sn17.24"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn17.24:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 17"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 17"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn17.24:0.2"
msgid "3. Tatiyavagga"
msgstr "3. The Third Chapter"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn17.24:0.3"
msgid "24. Ekadhītusutta"
msgstr "24. An Only Daughter"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn17.24:1.1"
msgid "Sāvatthiyaṃ viharati."
msgstr "At Sāvatthī."

msgctxt "sn17.24:1.2"
msgid "“Dāruṇo, bhikkhave, lābhasakkārasiloko … pe …"
msgstr "“Possessions, honor, and popularity are brutal …"

msgctxt "sn17.24:1.3"
msgid ""
"saddhā bhikkhave upāsikā ekaṃ dhītaraṃ piyaṃ manāpaṃ evaṃ sammā āyācamānā "
"āyāceyya:"
msgstr ""
"A faithful laywoman with a dear and beloved only daughter would rightly "
"appeal to her:"

msgctxt "sn17.24:1.4"
msgid ""
"‘tādisā, ayye, bhavāhi yādisā khujjuttarā ca upāsikā veḷukaṇḍakiyā ca "
"nandamātā’ti."
msgstr ""
"‘My darling, please be like the laywomen Khujjuttarā and Veḷukaṇṭakī, Nanda’"
"s mother.’"

msgctxt "sn17.24:1.5"
msgid ""
"Esā, bhikkhave, tulā etaṃ pamāṇaṃ mama sāvikānaṃ upāsikānaṃ, yadidaṃ "
"khujjuttarā ca upāsikā veḷukaṇḍakiyā ca nandamātā."
msgstr ""
"These are a standard and a measure for my female lay disciples, that is, the "
"laywomen Khujjuttarā and Veḷukaṇṭakī, Nanda’s mother."

msgctxt "sn17.24:1.6"
msgid "Sace kho tvaṃ, ayye, agārasmā anagāriyaṃ pabbajasi;"
msgstr ""
"‘But my darling, if you go forth from the lay life to homelessness, please "
"be like the nuns Khemā and Uppalavaṇṇā.’"

msgctxt "sn17.24:1.7"
msgid "tādisā, ayye, bhavāhi yādisā khemā ca bhikkhunī uppalavaṇṇā cāti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn17.24:1.8"
msgid ""
"Esā, bhikkhave, tulā etaṃ pamāṇaṃ mama sāvikānaṃ bhikkhunīnaṃ, yadidaṃ khemā "
"ca bhikkhunī uppalavaṇṇā ca."
msgstr ""
"These are a standard and a measure for my nun disciples, that is, the nuns "
"Khemā and Uppalavaṇṇā."

msgctxt "sn17.24:1.9"
msgid ""
"Mā ca kho tvaṃ, ayye, sekhaṃ appattamānasaṃ lābhasakkārasiloko anupāpuṇātūti."
msgstr ""
"‘And my darling, may you not come into possessions, honor, and popularity "
"while you’re still a trainee and haven’t achieved your heart’s desire.’"

msgctxt "sn17.24:1.10"
msgid ""
"Tañce, bhikkhave, bhikkhuniṃ sekhaṃ appattamānasaṃ lābhasakkārasiloko "
"anupāpuṇāti, so tassā hoti antarāyāya."
msgstr ""
"If a trainee who hasn’t achieved their heart’s desire comes into "
"possessions, honor, and popularity it’s an obstacle for them."

msgctxt "sn17.24:1.11"
msgid "Evaṃ dāruṇo kho, bhikkhave, lābhasakkārasiloko … pe …"
msgstr "So brutal are possessions, honor, and popularity. …”"

msgctxt "sn17.24:1.12"
msgid "evañhi vo, bhikkhave, sikkhitabban”ti."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn17.24:1.13"
msgid "Catutthaṃ."
msgstr ""
